'''陰陽司'''，尊稱為'''陰陽司公'''，是[[道教|道教]][[神祇|神祇]]，'''[[東嶽大帝|東嶽大帝]]'''、'''[[五福王爺|五福王爺]]'''、'''[[城隍|城隍]]'''等[[陰間|陰間]]神明的輔吏。<ref name="a">{{cite news |title=陰陽公廟- 醫術精湛的陰陽都總管 |url=https://onemorestep11.adan.tw/yinyang-executive-temple |work=一步就出走 |date=10 May 2018 |language=zh-TW |accessdate=2021-08-14 |archive-date=2021-04-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210430233101/https://onemorestep11.adan.tw/yinyang-executive-temple |dead-url=no }}</ref>在[[城隍廟|城隍廟]]中，相當於[[城隍|城隍]]的[[秘書長|秘書長]]，協調城隍其餘幕僚諸[[司官|司官]]。<ref name="a"/><ref name="b">{{cite news |title=陰陽司公要出龕　鎖定寶神直播準沒錯 {{!}} 寶神 {{!}} 三立新聞網 |url=https://www.setn.com/m/ampnews.aspx?NewsID=787440 |work=SETN |date=29 July 2020 |language=zh |accessdate=2021-08-14 |archive-date=2021-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210814032623/https://www.setn.com/m/ampnews.aspx?NewsID=787440 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=彥昇 |first1=黃 |title=青山王的秘書長－陰陽司公 |url=https://bobee.nownews.com/20171116-15171/amp |work=保庇NOW |date=16 November 2017 |language=zh-TW |accessdate=2021-08-14 |archive-date=2021-04-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210429235831/https://bobee.nownews.com/20171116-15171/amp |dead-url=no }}</ref>

